Lib who manage a refresh token for oauth2 service with algorithm like https://github.com/defuse/php-encryption


Use this for make private.key and public.key:
$ echo "base64:$(cat /dev/random | head -c 32 | base64)" > password.cfg
$ openssl genrsa -traditional -out private.key 4096; # ssh-keygen -t rsa -b 4096 -m PEM -f private.key -N ''; rm private.key.pub;
$ openssl rsa -in private.key -pubout -out public.key;
